# Assets Directory

This directory is for app assets like icons, splash screens, etc.

The app currently works without any assets as it uses:
- Emojis for mood display
- Gradient backgrounds (programmatically generated)
- System fonts

If you want to add custom assets:
- icon.png (1024x1024) - App icon
- splash.png (1242x2436) - Splash screen
- adaptive-icon.png (1024x1024) - Android adaptive icon
- favicon.png (48x48) - Web favicon

These are optional - Expo will use defaults if not provided.

